trans-unit.source: Enumerates the elements of an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: Enumera gli elementi di un oggetto <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: To get an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract>, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A> method of an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract>.
trans-unit.target: Per ottenere un <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract>, utilizzare il <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A> metodo di un <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract>.

trans-unit.source: Returns the key and the value of the current <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> entry.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce la chiave e il valore della voce <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> corrente.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry" /> that contains the key and the value of the current <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> entry.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry" /> che contiene la chiave e il valore della voce <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> corrente.

trans-unit.source: After an enumerator is created or after the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> method is called, the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> method must be called to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before calling the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> method; otherwise, the return value of <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: Dopo la creazione di un enumeratore o dopo il <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> metodo viene chiamato, il <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> metodo deve essere chiamato per passare l'enumeratore al primo elemento della raccolta prima di chiamare il <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> metodo; in caso contrario, il valore restituito di <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> è definito.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> also throws an exception if the last call to <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, which indicates the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> Inoltre, genera un'eccezione se l'ultima chiamata a <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> restituito `false`, che indica la fine della raccolta.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> does not move the position of the enumerator, and consecutive calls to <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> return the same object until either <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> non modifica la posizione dell'enumeratore e le chiamate successive a <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract.GetEntry%2A> restituiscono lo stesso oggetto finché non <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> o <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> viene chiamato.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract" /> is positioned before the first entry of the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> or after the last entry.
trans-unit.target: L'oggetto <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract" /> viene posizionato prima della prima voce dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> o dopo l'ultima voce.

trans-unit.source: Returns the key of the current <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> entry.
